                "message": "Fix functools.wraps on cyfunctions on 3.14+\n\n... by providing basic `__annotate__` implementation.\n\nFixes #7675.\n\nThe issue is that in 3.14, wraps reassigns `__annotate__` rather\nthan `__annotations__`. The basic implementation I provide is\na function that just returns the `__annotations__` dictionary\n(stored at the time it was created),\nwhile setting `__annotate__` just calls the function and then\nsets the `__annotations__` to the result. This should also\nstand a decent chance of working with non-cyfunctions.",
